	Yay! Everything works! Since I finished a full two hours prior to the deadline, I added an extra feature: as a complement to the adversary, I've added the Mr. Happy slider bar, which gives you a chance of getting the piece that you most need. I've found that if you set it to about 10%, the even the LameBrain never loses. I had wanted to experiment in creating my own brain, but I ran out of time :-(. Maybe I'll play around with it later.